name: webanno.custom.IGComplexDataRelationship
description: Links components of complex data structure to ensure association

name: webanno.custom.IGComplexDataStructure

tag_set.name: IG Data Structure Annotations
tag_set.description:
Annotations to code complex non-collection data structures (e.g., individual objects, or elements of collections)
Example: a bit (qualifier) more than (comparator) 10 (quantity) tons (unit) high-quality (object property) building material (object)

tags.tag_description: Comparator in data structure expression (Example: MORE THAN 10 tons building material)
Descriptor of object/substance/artefact that is quantified or otherwise described
Property of Object described in complex data structure
Qualifier in expression (Example: SUFFICIENT building material - sufficient is the qualifier)
Quantity in data structure (Example: more than 10 tons building material - 10 is the quantity)
Unit expression in data structure (Example: more than 10 TONS building material - TONS is the unit)

description: Allows decomposition of complex non-collection data structures (see 'IG Collection Relationship' for collections)
